description:
Shonen Jump's feeling really Square this week thanks to the monthlies! In Blue Exorcist, Rin's fought countless demonic creatures and monsters, but this time around he's up against perhaps his toughest opponent...love! Also, the Jump Starts continue with another chapter of Red Sprite and Love Rush! All this, plus Seraph of the End and more in this week's issue!
